nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Negative Prompt)
widgets_values: Signature, deformed, smooth, plastic, blurry, grainy, ((hands)), ((hand))

instantid model: https://huggingface.co/InstantX/InstantID/resolve/main/ip-adapter.bin?download=true
(ComfyUI/models/instantid)

The main model can be downloaded from HuggingFace and should be placed into the ComfyUI/models/instantid directory. (Note that the model is called ip_adapter as it is based on the IPAdapter models).

checkpoint: https://civitai.com/models/215418?modelVersionId=273102
(ComfyUI/models/checkpoints)

If you change the checkpoint model, please adjust the cfg and steps in ksample yourself.

You can rewrite the prompt words to change the style of the picture, such as 
"analog photo, retro, a cute [black girl], outdoors, wild nature, hair oreola, hair ornaments, realistic detailed skin, film grain, raw photo, sunny day, flowers, ((shy weak smile)), (sharp focus:1.2), sun hat"
